sources.title: 1938 Der Maulkorb ( Ralph Arthur Roberts, Paul Henckels, Hilde Weissner, Theodor Loos)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1938. Der Maulkorb.  U.a mit Ralph Arthur Roberts und Paul Henckels

metadata.Plot: Dog owners in a town are asked to account for themselves when a muzzle is found subversively placed on a statue of the reigning duke.Leading up to a trial,the prosecuting attorney who was drunk at the time doesn't recall what he did.
metadata.Actors: Ralph Arthur Roberts, Hilde Weissner, Charlotte Schellhorn
